    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve truly babied it since day one! It still has that fresh, new-car feel and looks just like it did when it first rolled off the showroom floor. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve found it. I'm happy to answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out for a chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
