    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a mechanically peerless E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L powerplant with its signature individual throttle bodies and optimized double VANOS. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing service, ensuring structural and internal longevity. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual and a limited-slip differential. Every bushing, damper, and seal remains in factory-fresh condition, providing the tactile feedback and lateral grip this chassis is renowned for. Meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
