    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty in person\u2014it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, and it\u2019s in truly incredible shape inside and out. It drives like a total dream and has been kept tucked away in a garage its whole life. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Drop me a message and come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
