    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is a concours-level E46 M3, meticulously maintained for the discerning collector. This specimen features the high-revving S54 straight-six, with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS top-end overhaul to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis has been proactively addressed with a subframe reinforcement kit, mitigating the platform's known fatigue points. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. The suspension features refreshed bushings and OEM-plus dampers, maintaining original kinematics and damping profiles. With zero paint metered outside factory tolerances and a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment in analog performance engineering.",
